name: strong.justin.openinbrowser
title: Open in Browser
description: Version 1.1.0: Now saves before opening the file. If you like my work then let's work together, check out my resume: https://u.nu/13tp Version 1.0.0: Open in Browser is a Brackets extension which allows you to open a file from the Working Files pane in the default browser or application using a context menu or the keyboard shortcut CMD-2/CTRL-2.
author: Justin Strong
